strip grazing
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:break feeding, where grazing is restricted to small strips of pasture or crop by temporary fencing [normally without a back fence]
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
